                fnHowtoConnectionsTitle: 'Detailed connections — each one solves a problem',
                fnHowtoConnectionsHint: 'Click to expand: what it solves + how much business loses without it',
                fnHowtoMechanicsTitle: 'Three automatic mechanics',
                fnHowtoEscTitle: 'Escalation by hierarchy',
                fnHowtoEscDesc: 'The system knows where to escalate the problem. You get notified only when others can\'t resolve it without you.',
                fnHowtoEsc0: 'Task overdue → notify function owner',
