                fnHowtoWeeklyTitle: 'Weekly report to manager',
                fnHowtoWeeklyDesc: 'Every Monday at 9:00 each function owner automatically receives a report about their department. Without your involvement.',
                fnHowtoWeeklyTasks: 'Completed this week: X (comparison with last week)',
                fnHowtoWeeklyOverdue: 'Count + list — who needs to deal with it',
